      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 23.5,
      "text": "Now you're registering So pretty little thing that drives me wild Is the same thing that drives me up Then guys wild and tall",
      "start": 11.5
    },
    {
      "end": 35,
      "text": "Well it'd be beautiful for us to keep a donut, no, it says what we do, a butterfly, deep fly, you can't",
      "start": 23
    },
    {
      "end": 46.5,
      "text": "You can't hear this, come to a lie that you want me to do What you do go on and fly with those wings baby it's true to you my baby",
      "start": 34.5
    },
    {
      "end": 58,
      "text": "I don't know it, it's the right way to go But if you let it go, and you said it for your little bit",
      "start": 46
    },
    {
      "end": 69.5,
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 57.5
    },
    {
      "end": 81,
      "text": "The verse to give somebody else a feeling that I feel But why should I be so? Pain capable of sharing",
      "start": 69
    },
    {
      "end": 92.5,
      "text": "*music*",
      "start": 80.5
    },
    {
      "end": 104,
      "text": "I can't describe the way it feels when you are alive Never would I want you to dream",
      "start": 92
    },
    {
      "end": 115.5,
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 103.5
    },
    {
